# React & UI

## Components

- Functional components with explicit TypeScript prop interfaces
- Server Components for data fetch; `'use client'` only for interactivity
- Never mutate state objects — pure updates only

## Styling

- Tailwind; dark zinc background, orange primary CTAs
- Semantic colors: green success, amber progress/warning, red errors
- Shared shell via app layout components — match existing page widths

## Native (Capacitor)

Detect native via `SlidePressApp/` user agent or `window.WEBVIEW_SERVER_URL`. Native-only: haptics, bottom sheets, Save to Photos, pull-to-refresh, biometric lock. No Stripe checkout in native — RevenueCat IAP only.

## Performance

- React Compiler handles memoization — do not add manual memo wrappers
- Bulk Supabase inserts for slide arrays — no per-row loops in hot paths
